------------------------------------------------------------------------
Built on Superpowers
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Crucible is a workflow that runs on top of Superpowers
(https://github.com/obra/superpowers). It does not vendor or redistribute
Superpowers; it invokes Superpowers skills (writing-plans, brainstorming,
subagent-driven-development, using-git-worktrees, finishing-a-development-branch)
and the plan-document-reviewer / spec-document-reviewer / code-reviewer templates
at runtime. Superpowers must be installed separately (Crucible needs Superpowers
v5.1.0+, last tested against v6.0.3). Crucible is not
affiliated with or endorsed by the Superpowers project.

